    "1245": {
      "review_count": 22,
      "average_rating": 4.23,
      "html": "<div id=\"tab-reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--reviews panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div id=\"reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Reviews\"><div id=\"comments\"><h2 class=\"woocommerce-Reviews-title\">22 reviews for <span>Vyntech Matte Black Pods</span></h2><ol class=\"commentlist\">\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-801\">\n<div id=\"comment-801\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8a?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Rohit Verma</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Matte black finish ekdum killer hai. Airpods jaisa same design par black mein bahot premium lagta hai. ANC is also very decent for the price.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_63ec69dec0d040a2996441f1038002bb.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-802\">\n<div id=\"comment-802\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8b?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Anjali S.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Battery backup is exactly as advertised. I got around 8 hours on a single charge with ANC off. Deducting one star because the matte case catches smudges easily.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-803\">\n<div id=\"comment-803\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8c?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Srinivas Rao</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Sound chala bagundi, kani left earbud connect avvadaniki koncham time padutundi. Otherwise product is good.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Srinivas,<br><br>We apologize for the pairing delay. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and our product expert will help you run a quick firmware update to fix the left earbud sync issue.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-804\">\n<div id=\"comment-804\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Karthik N.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Here is my own review for this product: what I found. Initially my delivery was delayed and support agent was not responding properly. But I used the head contact in the support link and the issue was resolved same day. Got the product safely. The low latency mode is excellent for gaming.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_1263dfc292354337a4bbde3723e73b2f.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-805\">\n<div id=\"comment-805\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8e?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Mayank Patel</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>ANC is surprisingly good for the price. ENC works fine for indoor calls, but struggles a bit in heavy wind outside.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-806\">\n<div id=\"comment-806\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8f?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Tushar Desai</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Always wanted Airpods in black color and Vyntech finally delivered! The stealthy matte black looks amazing. Sound quality is top notch.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_69268fb26415482e8d25102ff9de35ce.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-807\">\n<div id=\"comment-807\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8g?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 2 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:40%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">2</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Arif Khan</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>The design is great but I have initiated a replacement because the right earbud battery drains in 2 hours. Waiting for pickup.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Arif,<br><br>We really apologize for the inconvenience caused by the defective battery. You need not worry, your replacement has been processed. Your brand new sealed product will be delivered to you at the time of pickup.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-808\">\n<div id=\"comment-808\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8h?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Saravanan K.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Romba nalla irukku. The 35 hours battery with the case is genuine. I haven't charged it since last week.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_87994c2cea60424d8891d99a8e42748d.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-809\">\n<div id=\"comment-809\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8i?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Nitin P.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Fitting is nice, it doesn't fall out during workouts. Bass is punchy but treble could be slightly better.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-810\">\n<div id=\"comment-810\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8j?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Prakash Jha</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Thoda heavy lagta hai kaan mein long use ke baad. ANC on rakhne se pressure feel hota hai.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Prakash,<br><br>We apologize for the discomfort. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and our product expert will gladly assist you in selecting the correct soft ear-tips and guide you on switching to \"Mild ANC\" mode to relieve the ear pressure.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-811\">\n<div id=\"comment-811\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8k?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Varun Das</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Absolutely brilliant. Call quality with ENC makes my office meetings so peaceful.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_b8d29ce5718b4aad8f7132b4243b66ec.jpeg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-812\">\n<div id=\"comment-812\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8l?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Riya Agarwal</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Awesome product for the price. Highly recommended to everyone looking for black pods.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-813\">\n<div id=\"comment-813\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8m?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Aditya Sharma</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Worth buying. Build quality is nice but the hinge feels a little delicate.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-814\">\n<div id=\"comment-814\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8n?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Sneha K.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Good sounding buds, but the touch controls take some getting used to.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-815\">\n<div id=\"comment-815\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8o?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Vikram Singh</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Sometimes it disconnects when my phone is in the other room. Range is only good up to 5-6 meters.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Vikram,<br><br>We apologize for the range issue. While walls can interfere with Bluetooth, 5 meters is below our standard. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and our team will check if your unit has a hardware defect and issue a swift replacement.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-816\">\n<div id=\"comment-816\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8p?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Gaurav T.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Best matte black earbuds in the market right now. The finish is so premium.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_df84e4393f914b4a81945b6191db437f.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" 